{"tid":1625091,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳準新娘李旻芳疑因政治表態遭無綫削減工作","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T08:05:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2100389780b01eed5bb41b1f31b00f76133b9bd6","tid":1625091,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:50:29.000Z","msg":"繼有「宅男女神」之稱的《東張西望》主持林泳淘疑因政治表態遭無綫提前解約後，有傳同樣有份主持《東張》的李旻芳也因為同一原因遭無綫暫停廠景主持的工作，無綫目前正研究是否要將其外景工作也取消，變相停職。李旻芳接受傳媒訪問時強調從未在政治上表態，也沒有收到公司通知工作有變，她表示其廠景主持工作多數是每隔一星期才做一次，非每星期都有。下月5日結婚的她表示因忙於籌備婚禮，已向公司申請了本月所有星期六及星期日放假，其餘日子均要開工。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20191005/s00009/0660cf1dc356cd0adf26a4065c66d72d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20191005%2Fs00009%2F0660cf1dc356cd0adf26a4065c66d72d.jpg&h=6d2bdac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191005/1570251591370/%E5%82%B3%E6%BA%96%E6%96%B0%E5%A8%98%E6%9D%8E%E6%97%BB%E8%8A%B3%E7%96%91%E5%9B%A0%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E9%81%AD%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E5%89%8A%E6%B8%9B%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20191005%2F1570251591370%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%25BA%2596%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A8%2598%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2597%25BB%25E8%258A%25B3%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2585%258B%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E5%2589%258A%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=3dc30688\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20191005%2F1570251591370%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%25BA%2596%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A8%2598%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2597%25BB%25E8%258A%25B3%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2585%258B%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E5%2589%258A%25E6%25B8%